title: Google\Cloud\Talent\V4beta1\Phone
name: Phone
description:
Resource that represents a person's telephone number.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.talent.v4beta1.Phone

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.usage
params.description: The usage of the phone. For example, SCHOOL, WORK, PERSONAL.

params.name: data.type
params.description: The phone type. For example, LANDLINE, MOBILE, FAX.

params.name: data.number
params.description: Phone number. Any phone formats are supported and only exact matches are performed on searches. For example, if a phone number in profile is provided in the format of "(xxx)xxx-xxxx", in profile searches the same phone format has to be provided. Number of characters allowed is 20.

params.name: data.when_available
params.description: When this number is available. Any descriptive string is expected. Number of characters allowed is 100.
